A truck carrying a chemical substance rolled on the N3 southbound near Lions River on Wednesday morning. Midlands EMS and police were on scene. According to Roland Robertson of the Midlands EMS, there were no injuries. Meanwhile, RTI spokesperson Zinhle Mali said the road has been closed on the N3 from Mooi River coming to Pietermaritzburg. "Vehicles are being diverted to Mount West as an alternative route," said Mali.